        "name": "Peng Tao",
        "email": "bergwolf@gmail.com",
        "username": "bergwolf"
      },
      "date": "2013-03-18 07:14:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nJeff, I only made the suggested change to liblustre build because for kernel build, if we define such macros in lustre, we'll have to make sure all files include the new macros header file _after_ including linux/posix_acl_xattr.h, and IMO we'd better not introduce header file dependency.",
